golf_courses.description: Adare Manor Golf Club provides a quality golfing experience, for members and visitors, on a uniquely scenic course, in a consistently friendly and welcoming manner. Our 18-hole parkland golf course is steeped in history and is recognised as one of the best hidden gems on the island of Ireland.

golf_courses.description: Situated just six miles from Dublin city centre, Leopardstown Golf Centre holds a unique position in terms of easy access and facilities. It is an 18 hole Pay as you Play golf course, incorporating a 74 bay floodlit driving range and is located in the centre of the racecourse, with access through Foxrock village entrance.
